<paragraph id="715FCC1AFFAFFF8FFF41B9EFEE8AE518" blockId="0.[136,1452,1682,1924]" pageId="0" pageNumber="116">
<collectionCode id="17F154DFFFAFFF8FFF41B9EFEDEEE4F5" box="[189,212,1717,1745]" country="China" lsid="urn:lsid:biocol.org:col:13092" name="Nanjing University" pageId="0" pageNumber="116" type="Herbarium">N</collectionCode>
<emphasis id="43941008FFAFFF8FFF29B9EDEC36E4F5" bold="true" box="[213,268,1719,1745]" pageId="0" pageNumber="116">otes:</emphasis>
— 
<taxonomicName id="B6E0B799FFAFFF8FFED4B9EDECA3E4F5" authorityName="Alston" authorityYear="1956" box="[296,409,1719,1745]" class="Polypodiopsida" family="Pteridaceae" genus="Afropteris" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" order="Polypodiales" pageId="0" pageNumber="116" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="43941008FFAFFF8FFED4B9EDECA3E4F5" box="[296,409,1719,1745]" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="116">Afropteris</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
consists of 
<taxonomicName id="B6E0B799FFAFFF8FFDE6B9EDEEC2E4F5" authority="(C. Christensen) Alston (1956: 5)" authorityName="Alston" authorityPageNumber="5" authorityYear="1956" baseAuthorityName="C. Christensen" box="[538,1016,1718,1745]" class="Polypodiopsida" family="Pteridaceae" genus="Afropteris" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" order="Polypodiales" pageId="0" pageNumber="116" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="repens">
<emphasis id="43941008FFAFFF8FFDE6B9EDEFB8E4F4" box="[538,642,1719,1745]" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="116">A. repens</emphasis>
(C. Christensen) 
<bibRefCitation id="1571B1EBFFAFFF8FFCBDB9ECEEC2E4F5" author="Alston, A. H. G." box="[833,1016,1718,1745]" pageId="0" pageNumber="116" pagination="5 - 27" refId="ref1402" refString="Alston, A. H. G. (1956) New African ferns. Boletim da Sociedade Broteriana, ser. 2 30: 5 - 27." type="journal article" year="1956">Alston (1956: 5)</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
of tropical West Africa and 
<taxonomicName id="B6E0B799FFAFFF8FFAD0B9EDEC9CE4D1" authority="(Baker) Alston (1956: 6)" authorityName="Alston" authorityPageNumber="6" authorityYear="1956" baseAuthorityName="Baker" class="Polypodiopsida" family="Pteridaceae" genus="Afropteris" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" order="Polypodiales" pageId="0" pageNumber="116" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="barklyae">
<emphasis id="43941008FFAFFF8FFAD0B9EDE891E4F4" box="[1324,1451,1718,1745]" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="116">A. barklyae</emphasis>
(Baker) 
<bibRefCitation id="1571B1EBFFAFFF8FFF1AB980EC9CE4D1" author="Alston, A. H. G." box="[230,422,1754,1781]" pageId="0" pageNumber="116" pagination="5 - 27" refId="ref1402" refString="Alston, A. H. G. (1956) New African ferns. Boletim da Sociedade Broteriana, ser. 2 30: 5 - 27." type="journal article" year="1956">Alston (1956: 6)</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
endemic to the 
<collectingCountry id="09F78C8AFFAFFF8FFD98B980EFE5E4D0" box="[612,735,1754,1780]" name="Seychelles" pageId="0" pageNumber="116">Seychelles</collectingCountry>
. The former was originally placed in 
<taxonomicName id="B6E0B799FFAFFF8FFB64B981E9E1E4D0" box="[1176,1243,1755,1780]" class="Polypodiopsida" family="Pteridaceae" genus="Pteris" kingdom="Plantae" order="Polypodiales" pageId="0" pageNumber="116" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="43941008FFAFFF8FFB64B981E9E1E4D0" box="[1176,1243,1755,1780]" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="116">Pteris</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, i.e., 
<taxonomicName id="B6E0B799FFAFFF8FFAE3B981ECA7E53D" authority="C. Christensen (1906: 606)" authorityName="C. Christensen" authorityPageNumber="606" authorityYear="1906" class="Polypodiopsida" family="Pteridaceae" genus="Afropteris" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" order="Polypodiales" pageId="0" pageNumber="116" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="repens">
<emphasis id="43941008FFAFFF8FFAE3B981E8B2E4D0" box="[1311,1416,1755,1780]" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="116">P. repens</emphasis>
C. 
<bibRefCitation id="1571B1EBFFAFFF8FFF74B9A4ECA7E53D" author="Christensen, C." box="[136,413,1790,1817]" pageId="0" pageNumber="116" refId="ref1458" refString="Christensen, C. (1906) Index filicum. H. Hagerup, Copenhagen." type="book" year="1906">Christensen (1906: 606)</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
. The latter is the only one that needs to be transferred to 
<taxonomicName id="B6E0B799FFAFFF8FFBD1B9A5E94AE53C" box="[1069,1136,1791,1816]" class="Polypodiopsida" family="Pteridaceae" genus="Pteris" kingdom="Plantae" order="Polypodiales" pageId="0" pageNumber="116" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="43941008FFAFFF8FFBD1B9A5E94AE53C" box="[1069,1136,1791,1816]" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="116">Pteris</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. It should be noted that the Barkly specimen was collected in 1864, not 1804 as sometime believed.
</paragraph>
